{"tid":672804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴女鄰居噪音　躁漢露鳥被斬","createTime":"2018-05-21T09:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T10:34:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce5202317e70dc7778f9858366b08224dc90807","tid":672804,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397002&d=udWQ8CAbBnyBdUhumdbJwF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3e60daac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397002&h=140b9c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397002</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月21日 <br />\n<br />\n投訴女鄰居噪音　躁漢露鳥被斬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/21la7p07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F21la7p07.jpg&h=3cbef4d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌葵芳邨兩名素有積怨鄰居，昨因小事爭執，繼而演變成露械、持刀傷人鬧劇。一名無業漢昨早到樓上單位投訴噪音，與開門迎戰的女鄰居吵架期間，突然裸露下體示威，遭女鄰居持菜刀追斬，幸僅受輕傷，送院敷治後無大礙。女鄰居涉傷人，他則涉「露械」，雙雙被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胸口手臂中刀<br />\n<br />\n「露鳥」被斬男子姓任（58歲），之前與母親同住，其後母親入住安老院，他獨居於葵芳邨葵德樓24樓一單位。消息稱，自99年搬入後，任經常投訴居住樓上一家四口發出噪音，先後報警20多次。<br />\n<br />\n昨早11時許，他因噪音上門大興問罪之師，與25樓單位46歲姓王女戶主爭吵。消息指雙方互數不是，其間任突然脫褲裸露下體，女戶主受辱後大怒，取出菜刀開門追斬，任走避不及胸口及手臂中三刀倒地。警方接報到場將傷者送院，經調查後以涉嫌傷人拘捕姓王女戶主，任則涉猥褻露體被捕，案件交由葵青警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n王的丈夫事後接受訪問時道出另一版本，他指樓下男戶主經常用錘子扑牆，又曾上門敲閘，兩年前更試過門前爆樽倒食油，驚動警方上門。他們向管理處投訴多次不果，半年前申請調遷，尚未獲安排之際，對方竟上門鬧事，更在妻子面前脫褲自慰，妻子被激怒才追斬。<br />\n<br />\n任昨晚返家休養（圖），但對事件不願多提，僅稱：「（傷口）唔痛！好小事啫！」<br />\n<br />\n■記者司徒韋桐  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n遊艇會火燒連環船　三警不適送院<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n私家車旺角鏟路四傷"},{"pid":"de550a1e31cc4c730fd7dd7d31cdb61ecff72550","tid":672804,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:04:04.000Z","msg":"葵涌果頭不嬲係痴線佬同癲婆集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3e2e7cf00da9275f7730aaae0960b7e4512aa1","tid":672804,"uid":182286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ab3686f4cc812e11f176f66b7878244e73b4506","tid":672804,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db3e2e7cf00da9275f7730aaae0960b7e4512aa1","tid":672804,"uid":182286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:13:28.000Z","msg":"屌公屋真係好撚多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21949c49a13d26059c23438e862d891d2c60f79","tid":672804,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"今舖真係任劍輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60607653aac85326114dbda94e2fc9eff2bd2bc7","tid":672804,"uid":166109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:16:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會個女人同露雀男派帽俾個老公，咁岩俾人發現而做既一場戲"},{"pid":"39da47546b617a8b1f66342480a0c2cf8c5a8842","tid":672804,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"持械 vs 露械  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2e6042d7a84065e7b5c6b11f6c46b610a12de5","tid":672804,"uid":21120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"肯定係兩個互屌<br />\n女鄰居叫個男人除褲啦"},{"pid":"fc1ead28e11c844c5515f245a9564c89bff17e67","tid":672804,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"樓上有細蚊仔住，多數嘈，屌你係度打波打關斗"},{"pid":"7a368590db50f2c71ceb26fdb8e4693441414aad"